{"tid":738224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港台曾志豪為節目爆粗致歉 網民：聽日唔使返工","createTime":"2018-07-11T11:06:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T16:15:54.000Z","uid":46328,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"870bbd29739533ba172d1b0b16cd55c4951d4df5","tid":738224,"uid":46328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:06:50.000Z","msg":"乜咁唔小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n港台第二台《瘋Show快活人》主持人曾志豪今早在主持節目時，唔記得閂咪，喺節目休息時段，佢咪後一句「XAuntie」出咗街，現時港台網頁不提供今日該節目嘅重溫，只寫下一句：「節目不作網上播放。 This programme webcast is not available」。港台事後話已經收到投訴，會跟進處理。<br />\n<br />\n有網民話，曾志豪開咪後公開道歉。佢事後話，當時正熱烈討論一啲話題，忘記閂咪，結果講咗啲大人同細路都唔應該聽嘅說話，所以向大家講對不起。<br />\n<br />\n節目嘅facebook專頁有很多網民留言，正負評均有。網民話：「又唔係有心嘅，細路未聽過粗口咩？咩咁大件事姐？」、「曾志豪今晚可以放心看英格蘭，明天不用返工」、「豪仔：X你老X乜嘢意思？」、「mic後拗咩拗到爆粗，同埋對邊個講？」、「罪不致死，佢都馬上道歉， 希望高層畀次機會豪仔。」其他網民在facebook亦分享了相關事件：「這樣質素的電台主持是應該要辭退的」、「這個電台主持公然在大氣電波說粗口，太過份了吧！」<br />\n<br />\n港台機構傳訊及節目標準總監伍曼儀回覆查詢就話，當時曾志豪因為在兩段宣傳聲帶之間「開錯咪」、「撳錯掣」，「佢開咗自己個咪」，而當時曾志豪做緊一啲「好忟憎」嘅事，「（粗口）佢係鬧緊佢自己」，當曾志豪知道「開錯咪」、粗口「出咗街」後，已喺節目中兩次道歉。<br />\n<br />\n伍曼儀承認事後收到投訴，會跟進處理，相信通訊事務管理局稍後都會就事件聯絡港台，佢喺節目後已經責成曾志豪「表現唔專業」，「佢作為一個咁受歡迎嘅主持，佢咪前咪後都應該要小心自己嘅言語。」對於節目如今喺網上面無法重溫，伍曼儀就話稍後會上載無粗口嘅乾淨版，至於曾志豪聽日仲有無得開咪，佢就話暫時未聽到出有懲處嘅決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180711/58428460\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180711%2F58428460&d=DMF7AYdI%2B%2FHnh5No5QpxQZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=87395c80\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180711%2F58428460&h=30499232\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180711/58428460</a><br />\n<br />\n原片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hQRUh-4bBhA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhQRUh-4bBhA&d=DMF7AYdI%2B%2FHnh5No5QpxQZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7e1cfca0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hQRUh-4bBhA</a>"},{"pid":"174e5720cfb2b3aeb743933b49eed26b49c5c9b6","tid":738224,"uid":109983,"like":15,"dislike":13,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:10:11.000Z","msg":"炒鳩佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ad8424e725d80cae59c3f8ebbb810652b5d704","tid":738224,"uid":124020,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:11:45.000Z","msg":"Live 聽到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c83f0841ba2c2a3e175223914e66d94bf79b21f","tid":738224,"uid":10998,"like":66,"dislike":3,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:12:12.000Z","msg":"這樣質素的電台主持是應該要辭退的」、「這個電台主持公然在大氣電波說粗口，太過份了吧！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n實係嗰班癈中藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4be100bfbd21c900931285c28b758639fa780e","tid":738224,"uid":27251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"578d2dbd0962ed39e0da85b92fad67305bf8ee43","tid":738224,"uid":135313,"like":58,"dislike":7,"score":51,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:12:24.000Z","msg":"曾志豪做頭條新聞成日串鳩建制狗同無能正苦 可想而知想佢收皮無得做嘅係邊一類人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45afac5d25ee166d5ce3363e19a32bbcc6eeb3f","tid":738224,"uid":124020,"like":15,"dislike":3,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T11:12:44.000Z","msg":"不過二台無埋曾志豪不如執左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6c2e06986f0b2306f8fa10ae228a7a233a9ba3","tid":738224,"uid":23891,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0