br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1406464-20180711.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1406464-20180711.htm&d=DMF7AYdI%2B%2FHnh5No5QpxQZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=e586d262\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1406464-20180711.htm&h=66accf26\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1406464-20180711.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1406464_1_L_20180711193619.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1406464_1_L_20180711193619.jpg&h=19e421b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港電台節目主持人曾志豪早上在節目中說粗口。港台機構傳訊及節目標準組總監伍曼儀表示，曾志豪早上在一個節目中，播放宣傳聲帶時「開錯咪」，說了「不適合說話」，由明日起暫停曾志豪主持電台節目，直至本月22日。<br />\n<br />\n伍曼儀說，港台已即時嚴正處理，並訓斥對方主持節目不專業，港台就事件致歉。"},{"pid":"ac4b02658e97f31f4dda75d7bd6428267e23a562","tid":738224,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T14:54:33.000Z","msg":"左膠豪抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"befbe461392afabf6d937441068fb3fd1de49e10","tid":738224,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T14:55:26.000Z","msg":"劉慧卿-一比市民批評就話人語言暴力無資格講言論自由<br />\n曾志豪- 成日屈本土派納粹法西斯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係講粗口本身嚴重<br />\n而係根據曾志豪標準,條友應該立即resign"}]}